dc:description: Rim diameter 2.5 cm.  Base diameter 15.6 cm.  Rounded rimless top edge with one side higher than another.  Tall neck has straight sides, that broaden out to sloping shoulder and ovoid body.  Base is deeply concave and has pontil mark.  Thread decoration winds around vessel from top to base of neck.
One stress crack, one granule impurity in glass (on shoulder), frosting and bubbling throughout.
